==French==
===Etymology===
Old French [[avuec]], from vulgar Latin ''*abhocque'', from Latin [[ab hoc]] ‘whence, after which, jointly’.  Gradually supplanted Old French [[od]] ‘with’.

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/avɛk/}}
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /a.vEk/

===Preposition===
'''avec'''
# [[with]]

